title: Stanford Accounts
body:
Accounts









more info
stanfordyou






 



Create a
							new SUNet ID, the official Stanford University account.Pending
						account? Use the Status

Manage your SUNet ID
						settings: password changes, alias management,

							etc.




 



Forgot
                            password? You can reset your
                            SUNet ID password with this helper.
                    



 



Lost your two-step device? You can generate
                            a one-time two-step authentication code with this helper.
